lead_paragraph: Ireland skipper Robbie Keane cannot guarantee he will be fully fit to face Sweden in his country's first match of the European Championship but has no doubts he will be ready for the game against Belgium five days later.

headline.print_headline: Keane Says Will Be Fit to Face Belgium at Euro 2016
headline.main: Keane Says Will Be Fit to Face Belgium at Euro 2016
